en_153495_0	Kosgoda Police have initiated investigations looking into an incident where a fisherman allegedly gave a death threat to Balapitiya Divisional Secretary.
en_153495_1	The secretary was on an official visit to Kosgoda yesterday, to inspect fishing nets being used.
en_153495_2	Police said that an individual, who was waiting on the beach made the threat at knife point.
en_153495_3	Later, police arrested the suspect.
en_153495_4	He will be produced before Balapitiya Magistrate today.
